race.comment: HASTA LA WIZARD (2) was a new acquisition for the Nicole Irwin team last start when he made ground to run into third over 1360m at this track. Backs up quickly and is ready to fire. HEDGED YOUR BETS (3) went forward last start over 1050m at this track and held on well for third, beaten a neck. In a suitable race and can play a major role. SAUNTERING (6) is a gelding by Sir Prancealot out of Foie Gras on debut. Well educated with four trials. Among the leading chances. MEHIRAKOOL (9) was well back in transit when second up last start before finding the line nicely to grab fourth over this track and trip. Blinkers are removed. Should run well.
